  "Cauliflower":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit: purée cream, rice substitute, roast caramel, raw shave crunch, fry crisp — veg as starch mimic, sauce body, or texture layer.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nBlend / purée → Cream → Sauce, soup body\nRice / crumb → Grain sub → Bowl, pilaf\nRoast / char → Caramel nutty → Side, steak\nShave raw → Crunch → Salad, slaw\nFry → Crisp bite → Snack, garnish\n\nRoles: neutral canvas · bulk · crunch"},
  "Sweet Potatoes":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit: crisp cubes, mash, thin chips/coins, purée thickener, roast depth — starch as base, texture, body, or sweetness vs savory.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nCube + roast / crisp → Bite / base → Bowl, hash\nMash → Creamy carrier → Side, topping\nSlice thin → Chips / coins → Crunch layer\nBlend → Thickener → Sauce, soup\nRoast whole / wedge → Sweet depth → Balance acid/heat\n\nRoles: starch backbone · natural sweetness"},
