  "Chicken Thigh":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Chicken Thigh): sear skin, confit-ish braise, strip — dark poultry as forgiving fat + crisp.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSkin-down sear → Crisp skin → Plate\nBone-in roast / braise → Juicy pull → Bowl\nStrip / dice → Fast pieces → Stir-fry, taco\n\nRoles: juicy poultry · flavor fat"},
  "Chicken Breast":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit: slice thin (fast protein), dice (even bowl), grind (filling), poach-shred (soft salad), pound cutlet (crust) — same SKU, different functional roles.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSlice thin → Fast-cook protein → Stir-fry, sear\nDice small → Even cooking → Bowl, pasta\nGrind → Chicken mince → Meatballs, filling\nPoach + shred → Soft protein → Salad, sandwich\nPound thin → Cutlet → Crispy dishes\n\nPrimary: lean anchor — surface area beats dryness."},
  "Salmon Fillet":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Salmon Fillet): skin sear, steam, poach, flake — fish as delicate protein + optional crisp skin; overcooking kills the role.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nPan-sear skin-down → Crisp + moist → Plate fish\nSteam / gentle heat → Even gentle → Health-forward\nFlake → Tender pieces → Salad, cake, taco\nDice raw (if safe) → Tartare / poke → Cold apps\nCitrus / butter finish → Bright / rich → Sauce tie-in\n\nRoles: protein · delicate texture"},
  "Ground Beef":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Ground Beef): brown crumbles/patties; sauce body; filling binder; spice carrier — already minced so surface area is your speed lever.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nBrown crumble → Maillard bits → Sauce, taco, rice\nPatty / ball → Even cook → Burger, meatball\nRaw mix-in → Binder + fat → Dumpling, loaf\nSeason heavy → Flavor carrier → Chili, ragu\n\nRoles: fat + protein · quick cook"},
  "Shrimp":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Shrimp): quick high heat or gentle steam — protein as snap/tender bite; chop for filling if needed.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSear / grill → Caramel shell → Main protein\nSteam / simmer → Juicy → Broth, pasta\nChop / fold → Pieces → Filling, fried rice\nShell stock (if applicable) → Depth → Bisque, sauce\n\nRoles: briny protein · fast window"},
  "Scallops":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Scallops): quick high heat or gentle steam — protein as snap/tender bite; chop for filling if needed.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSear / grill → Caramel shell → Main protein\nSteam / simmer → Juicy → Broth, pasta\nChop / fold → Pieces → Filling, fried rice\nShell stock (if applicable) → Depth → Bisque, sauce\n\nRoles: briny protein · fast window"},
  "Pork Tenderloin":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Pork Tenderloin): medallion, butterfly, sear, quick braise — lean muscle as portion protein.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nMedallion sear → Even disk → Plate\nButterfly → Thin cutlet → Fast cook\nSlice strip → Stir-fry → Bowl\nQuick braise → Moist trade → Less crust\n\nRoles: tender muscle · easy to overcook"},
  "Duck Breast":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Duck Breast): medallion, butterfly, sear, quick braise — lean muscle as portion protein.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nMedallion sear → Even disk → Plate\nButterfly → Thin cutlet → Fast cook\nSlice strip → Stir-fry → Bowl\nQuick braise → Moist trade → Less crust\n\nRoles: tender muscle · easy to overcook"},
  "Lamb Chop":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Lamb Chop): medallion, butterfly, sear, quick braise — lean muscle as portion protein.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nMedallion sear → Even disk → Plate\nButterfly → Thin cutlet → Fast cook\nSlice strip → Stir-fry → Bowl\nQuick braise → Moist trade → Less crust\n\nRoles: tender muscle · easy to overcook"},
  "Bacon":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Bacon): crisp for texture, raw wrap for salt, render fat for cooking medium.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nCrisp → Crunch garnish → Salad, soup top\nWrap / layer → Salt + fat → Proteins, veg\nRender → Flavored oil → Start sautés\nChop fine → Umami bits → Finish\n\nRoles: salt · fat · crisp"},
  "Parmesan":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Parmesan): melt, crisp, whip, crumble, or finish — dairy as fat, tang, or texture layer.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nMelt → Bind / stretch → Pizza, gratin\nCrumble / shave → Salt burst → Salad, pasta\nWhip / fold → Air + fat → Frosting, mousse\nPan-crisp (halloumi-style) → Crunch → Garnish\nCultured tang → Balance richness → Sauce, dip\n\nRoles: fat · salt · tang"},
