  "Turkey Breast":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Turkey Breast): slice, dice, grind, cutlet, poach-shred — lean white meat as fast protein vs soft filler.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSlice thin → Fast protein → Stir-fry, sear\nPound cutlet → Even thin → Schnitzel-style\nDice → Even bowl pieces → Fried rice, pasta\nGrind → Lean filling → Meatball, dumpling\nPoach + shred → Soft → Salad, sandwich\n\nRoles: lean anchor · dries if mishandled"},
  "Whole Chicken":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Whole Chicken): breakdown beats whole-roast on short clock — parts sear, breast slice, leg braise.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nJoint → Parts cook at different speeds → Even finish\nBreast slice → Portion protein → Salad, sandwich\nLeg / thigh braise → Tender → Stew, taco\nCarcass → Stock body → Sauce, soup (if time)\n\nRoles: whole bird · multiple products"},
  "Chicken Wings":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Chicken Wings): sear skin, confit-ish braise, strip — dark poultry as forgiving fat + crisp.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSkin-down sear → Crisp skin → Plate\nBone-in roast / braise → Juicy pull → Bowl\nStrip / dice → Fast pieces → Stir-fry, taco\n\nRoles: juicy poultry · flavor fat"},
  "Cornish Hen":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Cornish Hen): breakdown beats whole-roast on short clock — parts sear, breast slice, leg braise.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nJoint → Parts cook at different speeds → Even finish\nBreast slice → Portion protein → Salad, sandwich\nLeg / thigh braise → Tender → Stew, taco\nCarcass → Stock body → Sauce, soup (if time)\n\nRoles: whole bird · multiple products"},
  "Ground Turkey":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Ground Turkey): brown crumbles/patties; sauce body; filling binder; spice carrier — already minced so surface area is your speed lever.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nBrown crumble → Maillard bits → Sauce, taco, rice\nPatty / ball → Even cook → Burger, meatball\nRaw mix-in → Binder + fat → Dumpling, loaf\nSeason heavy → Flavor carrier → Chili, ragu\n\nRoles: fat + protein · quick cook"},
  "Ground Pork":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Ground Pork): brown crumbles/patties; sauce body; filling binder; spice carrier — already minced so surface area is your speed lever.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nBrown crumble → Maillard bits → Sauce, taco, rice\nPatty / ball → Even cook → Burger, meatball\nRaw mix-in → Binder + fat → Dumpling, loaf\nSeason heavy → Flavor carrier → Chili, ragu\n\nRoles: fat + protein · quick cook"},
  "Pork Belly":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Pork Belly): collagen cut — slice/grind/shave vs long braise; form defines eating experience (honest time).",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nShave / pull → Soft strands → Taco, sandwich\nGrind → Filling / patty → Fast chew fix\nDice + braise → Partial tender → Chili, stew\nLow slice sear → Crust bite → Thin only\nRender trim fat → Cooking medium → Flavor base\n\nRoles: rich protein · time-dependent"},
  "Pork Chop":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit (Pork Chop): medallion, butterfly, sear, quick braise — lean muscle as portion protein.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nMedallion sear → Even disk → Plate\nButterfly → Thin cutlet → Fast cook\nSlice strip → Stir-fry → Bowl\nQuick braise → Moist trade → Less crust\n\nRoles: tender muscle · easy to overcook"},
