  "Brisket":{ingredientToolkitAi:"Toolkit: thin sear (fast crust), grind (burger/sauce body), shave (sandwich), dice braise (stew), render trim fat (flavor oil) — collagen beef becomes different eating experiences by form.",ingredientToolkit:"Ingredient toolkit (transform → result → use)\nSlice thin → Fast steak bite → Hot sear, taco\nGrind → Ground protein → Burgers, sauces, filling\nShave → Cheesesteak style → Sandwich, rice bowl\nDice small → Quick braise → Stew, chili\nRender fat (trim) → Cooking fat → Sauté, roux start\n\nPrimary: tough collagen — honesty on time still applies."},
